    {
        "url": "/quotes/molly_antopol_728507",
        "quote": "I've always loved short stories. Even before I was a writer, I was reading short stories - there were certain writers where I just felt like they could do in a short story what so many writers needed a whole novel to do, and that was really inspiring to me.",
